title: Name 5 Football Players
description: Who’s more famous: Aaron Rodgers or Shailene Woodley? Katie calls a sportsless friend for insight (s/o PJ Vogt). An update on last week (19:15). A long discussion about haircuts (38:50). Is Tom Brady the greatest athlete of all time (1:00:40)? The Mahomes family vs. the internet (1:08:55). Taunting peacefully (1:18:25). A review of The Weeknd’s halftime performance/an episode of Saved by the Bell (1:42:30). Was there a single good commercial (1:53:10)? Finally, advice on what to do after you fail (2:09:25).
